data.title: Donate your car to support NPR using the Car Talk Vehicle Donation Program
data.meta_description: Donate a car to NPR using the Car Talk Vehicle Donation Program by picking a radio station and filling out a simple form.
data.text: Please describe your vehicle (year, make, model, etc) What do you consider the value of your donation? Are you able to drop this off to a local auction facility? Does this boat include the trailer? Is your RV driveable? Would you be willing to accept an under $500 tax receipt? What is your name? What is your email address?
